data.description: Welcome to this stunning residence nestled within Westcott Plantation, where luxurious living meets the tranquility of a golf course setting. This beautiful home offers an abundance of space and exquisite features, making it the perfect retreat for those seeking both comfort and elegance. As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the seamless flow of the open-concept floor plan, accentuated by the warm embrace of wood floors that stretch throughout the downstairs living areas. The elegant foyer leads you to a versatile space, a combination of a formal dining room and living area, ideal for hosting intimate gatherings or special occasions. The heart of the home boasts a cozy yet sophisticated gas fireplace, adding a touch of ambiance and warmth to the living area.Adjacent to the living space is the a dream kitchen adorned with sleek tile. This space is equipped with modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a layout that invites culinary exploration.  Retreat to the second level where four generously sized bedrooms await, each exuding comfort and space. The master suite, in particular, offers a private enclave for rejuvenation with its thoughtful design and ample natural light.  Stepping outside to your screened porch and see beautiful views of the golf course. The expansive fenced backyard offers a sense of seclusion and granting you the luxury of privacy.  Rest assured, the home's infrastructure is equally impressive. The roof, a mere five years old, showcases durability and modern design with architectural shingles. An irrigation system ensures the lushness of your surroundings, while the recently installed tankless water heater guarantees an uninterrupted supply of hot water, enhancing efficiency and convenience. In every corner, this exquisite home showcases craftsmanship and design, ensuring a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and a harmonious connection to the lush outdoors. Don't miss this opportunity to make this exceptional residence your own and experience the epitome of refined living in Westcott Plantation.
